                    <li><i class="fa-li fa fa-check-square"></i>Purchase livestock from anywhere in Nigeria and have it delivered to your doorstep.</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-li fa fa-check-square"></i>Filter livestock options by breed, weight, color, age, and sex for tailored purchases.</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-li fa fa-check-square"></i>Track purchased livestock seamlessly from farm to plate for transparency and accountability.</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-li fa fa-check-square"></i>Secure online payment</li>
                    <li><i class="fa-li fa fa-check-square"></i>Fast and stress-free delivery.</li>
                </ul> 
